results.name: Decimal expansion of a constant related to A255359.
formula: Equals 2*Pi*exp(-3*Zeta(5)/Pi^4) * Product_{n>=1} ((n^4)!/stirling(n^4)), where stirling(n^4) = sqrt(2*Pi) * n^(4*n^4 + 2) / exp(n^4) is the Stirling approximation of (n^4)! and Zeta(5) = A013663. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Apr 20 2016
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Feb 24 2015
